<h1>Let's verify your account</h1>

<p>
  Welcome to MOSSLET! We're excited to have you join our community of privacy-conscious users.
</p>

<p>
  To complete your registration and start enjoying social media without the stress, anxiety, or tracking, please verify your account by clicking the button below:
</p>

<EmailComponents.button_centered to={@url} color="teal" size="lg">
  Verify Your Account
</EmailComponents.button_centered>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.status type="info">
  <strong>🔒 Your Privacy Matters:</strong>
  Unlike other platforms, we'll never sell your data, track you across the web, or use psychological manipulation to keep you scrolling.
</EmailComponents.status>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<p>Once verified, you'll be able to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>📱 Share updates with friends and family privately</li>
  <li>💬 Send end-to-end encrypted messages</li>
  <li>🛡️ Control exactly what you share and with whom</li>
  <li>🧘 Experience calm notifications that respect your time</li>
</ul>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.top_border>
  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    If you're having trouble clicking the verification button, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:
    <a href={@url}>{@url}</a>
  </EmailComponents.small_text>

  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    If you didn't create an account with MOSSLET, you can safely ignore this email.
  </EmailComponents.small_text>
</EmailComponents.top_border>
